    <texts>
      <txt c="X" s="1" y="200" x="100">This section should give a short introduction to:</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" x="130">Health Control Requirements</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" x="130">Various Hazard Sources</txt>
    </texts>
    <soundTexts>
      <sndTxt>
      </sndTxt>
      <sndTxt>
      </sndTxt>
      <sndTxt>In this section we are going to look more closely at health and safety factors the seaman should take notice of in his daily work, Health control requirements in the company, Local port state and flag state and Various hazard sources that may harmfully affect the employee’s health.</sndTxt>
    </soundTexts>
